{"tid":2030551,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港旗設計]一支國旗，最緊要係有人認同","createTime":"2020-05-22T22:11:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T12:22:01.000Z","uid":62721,"like":26,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"fe0f2b0d2eb4d23991616ec6a40852d1aa9a539d","tid":2030551,"uid":62721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T22:11:49.000Z","msg":"見到各位巴打設計嘅旗都好靚，好有意思<br />\n黃黑又好，藍白又好，龍獅旗又好<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GQcHxhM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGQcHxhM.png&h=5bb178bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mM831a8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmM831a8.png&h=d009ebaf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n5kqu4t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn5kqu4t.jpg&h=25653510&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但大家要反思一下一支國旗最緊要係咩？純粹係設計靚？ 係要有人認受，有歸屬感<br />\n唔通中國國旗靚啲你就會自認中國人？<br />\n<br />\n我地依家係要爭取最多人認同，唔係200萬份之幾萬連登仔認同，要We connect 先係贏<br />\n<br />\n所以，我認為香港旗先係最適合<br />\n可以係有英國國旗版本或者只用香港盾徽版本<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SquZzxe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSquZzxe.png&h=00c85e86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人可能會話，有英國國旗係戀殖，其實要認清世界上好多國家都係呢款旗，從來無人咁話澳洲紐西蘭<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VE4nxdB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVE4nxdB.png&h=cd6c7e44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y1H8sMR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy1H8sMR.png&h=3793814e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冇米字旗版本（龍獅旗）更可以代表新香港，已經唔係殖民地但依然保持象徵自由嘅貴族藍色底，優良的西方文明價值及體系<br />\n<br />\n係黃嘅上一代（1950~1980年代出生）都好容易接受到，因為由細見到大<br />\n就算藍絲都唔會極抗拒，仲可能聯想到魚翅撈飯嘅黃金時期<br />\n<br />\n至於90後，00後嘅後生仔，可能冇感覺，可能無認知<br />\n但都可以睇多啲，香港同紐約倫敦齊名最威水嘅年代就係用緊呢支旗，國際間都一定有印象<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/香港旗\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%97%97&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CIgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=0b318e47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/香港旗</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/龍獅旗\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E9%BE%8D%E7%8D%85%E6%97%97&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CIgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=5b388858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/龍獅旗</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢種貴族藍更加可以代表本土， 連最先提出本土主義嘅本民前都係用呢種藍做底色<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3q7kiTp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3q7kiTp.jpg&h=58331011&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>梁天琦：政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法，認同自己的方向。<br />\n各位手足，希望你地明白！</strong><br />\n以下開放理性討論，多多留言表達意見<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">TLDR懶人包： 一支好嘅香港旗（政治）係要爭取最多人認同，上一代同國際都對舊香港旗有認知有感覺，應該base on舊香港旗做更改或者沿用</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 龍獅旗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 舊香港旗<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n香港獨立，唯一出路！"},{"pid":"a28cfc73fb3fc1209f31508ca49da2eb5affd539","tid":2030551,"uid":282494,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T22:13:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HinwqFD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHinwqFD.jpg&h=a1962df3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa2633b664a3b64359be415d6b67c29b6a8d6214","tid":2030551,"uid":316927,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T22:13:12.000Z","msg":"有union jack就一定唔認同"},{"pid":"b7ec1dc3fca9f0465d9f12c053d1c80541db6607","tid":2030551,"uid":199902,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a28cfc73fb3fc1209f31508ca49da2eb5affd539","tid":2030551,"uid":282494,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T22:13:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HinwqFD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHinwqFD.jpg&h=a1962df3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T22:15:09.000Z","msg":"諗起國民黨，不了<br />\n台灣人都唔係個個都鍾意呢支旗啦"},{"pid":"fb333fa79e6b2e9bd3fe23a9cc62d347449f591a","tid":2030551,"uid":62721,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T22:16:30.000Z","msg":"仲有，光復香港，時光革命 呢句口號<br />\n本身就含有極強嘅本土意味<br />\n係由主張香港獨立嘅本民前提出<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/梁天琦\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E6%A2%81%E5%A4%A9%E7%90%A6&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CIgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=0e8fcdd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/梁天琦</a><br />\n<br />\n我相信香港人已經準備好，只係唔敢行動<br />\n我地係需要一支旗去代表左先，之後再諗點行動"},{"pid":"0f645e04e4b10fecb4ca92b319a0f5dd8b15e49e","tid":2030551,"uid":62721,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"aa2633b664a3b64359be415d6b67c29b6a8d6214","tid":2030551,"uid":316927,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T22:13:12.000Z","msg":"有union jack就一定唔認同"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T22:17:38.000Z","msg":"所以，無米字版本可以做到差唔多效果"},{"pid":"09b8b1c14f63da4491174bdd34feddf6fdbbb198","tid":2030551,"uid":56015,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fb333fa79e6b2e9bd3fe23a9cc62d347449f591a","tid":2030551,"uid":62721,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T22:16:30.000Z","msg":"仲有，光復香港，時光革命 呢句口號<br />\n本身就含有極強嘅本土意味<br />\n係由主張香港獨立嘅本民前提出<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/梁天琦\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E6%A2%81%E5%A4%A9%E7%90%A6&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CIgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=0e8fcdd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/梁天琦</a><br />\n<br />\n我相信香港人已經準備好，只係唔敢行動<br />\n我地係需要一支旗去代表左先，之後再諗點行動"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T22:18:42.000Z","msg":"唔好搞旗住啦"},{"pid":"7472775e93cffe017e92b6e9f5f19aba03f016ba","tid":2030551,"uid":210009,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T22:18:49.000Z","msg":"true<br />\n你拎得支旗出黎，國際就會望住你支旗<br />\n你今日求求其其整支黃黑旗出黎<br />\n全世界就會望住你支旗<br />\n他日獨立之後就會真係變成香港國旗<br />\n咁係唔係應該要嚴謹少少？至少俾多少少時間設計<br />\n唔係好似中學生咁求其用小畫家整兩pat色上去<br />\n跟手好浪漫咁話咁樣即係黎明來到要光復這香港就算<br />\n如果真的要整，係唔係應該都要有大部分香港人共識去一齊揀<br />\n你係想用黎表達對獨立嘅渴求嘅話，個人認為用返香港獨立旗就夠，訴求清晰簡單易明<br />\n真係獨立左之後先搵D真係識設計嘅人去設計國旗<br />\n而唔係你地班連登小朋友圍威喂畫完就拎出黎"},{"pid":"8cee5adaca2837514a94145db4e113f8451f42ee","tid":2030551,"uid":282494,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"b7ec1dc3fca9f0465d9f12c053d1c80541db6607","tid":2030551,"uid":199902,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a28cfc73fb3fc1209f31508ca49da2eb5affd539","tid":2030551,"uid":282494,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T22:13:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HinwqFD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHinwqFD.jpg&h=a1962df3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T22:15:09.000Z","msg":"諗起國民黨，不了<br />\n台灣人都唔係個個都鍾意呢支旗啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T22:19:46.000Z","msg":"中共唔代表中國<br />\n國民黨唔代表台灣<br />\n我們都是中華民族"},{"pid":"27b1335b5c8890988eea39b30127244ebf0f78cf","tid":2030551,"uid":56015,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7472775e93cffe017e92b6e9f5f19aba03f016ba","tid":2030551,"uid":210009,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T22:18:49.000Z","msg":"true<br />\n你拎得支旗出黎，國際就會望住你支旗<br />\n你今日求求其其整支黃黑旗出黎<br />\n全世界就會望住你支旗<br />\n他日獨立之後就會真係變成香港國旗<br />\n咁係唔係應該要嚴謹少少？至少俾多少少時間設計<br />\n唔係好似中學生咁求其用小畫家整兩pat色上去<br />\n跟手好浪漫咁話咁樣即係黎明來到要光復這香港就算<br />\n如果真的要整，係唔係應該都要有大部分香港人共識去一齊揀<br />\n你係想用黎表達對獨立嘅渴求嘅話，個人認為用返香港獨立旗就夠，訴求清晰簡單易明<br />\n真係獨立左之後先搵D真係識設計嘅人去設計國旗<br />\n而唔係你地班連登小朋友圍威喂畫完就拎出黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T22:20:54.000Z","msg":"咪係囉，仲有光時旗呢<br />\n用字係臨時性質，但最少無乜爭抝先"},{"pid":"1e5d9b0fca38b1febc1a336a41bcda64e1a62c26","tid":2030551,"uid":56015,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8cee5adaca2837514a94145db4e113f8451f42ee","tid":2030551,"uid":282494,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"b7ec1dc3fca9f0465d9f12c053d1c80541db6607","tid":2030551,"uid":199902,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a28cfc73fb3fc1209f31508ca49da2eb5affd539","tid":2030551,"uid":282494,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T22:13:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HinwqFD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHinwqFD.jpg&h=a1962df3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T22:15:09.000Z","msg":"諗起國民黨，不了<br />\n台灣人都唔係個個都鍾意呢支旗啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T22:19:46.000Z","msg":"中共唔代表中國<br />\n國民黨唔代表台灣<br />\n我們都是中華民族"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T22:22:00.000Z","msg":"中國都不了，中華民國都係咁話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同台灣做好朋友可以"},{"pid":"79c3befda629f964f7bf2ac9d15de5d90b2c00f8","tid":2030551,"uid":62721,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7472775e93cffe017e92b6e9f5f19aba03f016ba","tid":2030551,"uid":210009,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T22:18:49.000Z","msg":"true<br />\n你拎得支旗出黎，國際就會望住你支旗<br />\n你今日求求其其整支黃黑旗出黎<br />\n全世界就會望住你支旗<br />\n他日獨立之後就會真係變成香港國旗<br />\n咁係唔係應該要嚴謹少少？至少俾多少少時間設計<br />\n唔係好似中學生咁求其用小畫家整兩pat色上去<br />\n跟手好浪漫咁話咁樣即係黎明來到要光復這香港就算<br />\n如果真的要整，係唔係應該都要有大部分香港人共識去一齊揀<br />\n你係想用黎表達對獨立嘅渴求嘅話，個人認為用返香港獨立旗就夠，訴求清晰簡單易明<br />\n真係獨立左之後先搵D真係識設計嘅人去設計國旗<br />\n而唔係你地班連登小朋友圍威喂畫完就拎出黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T22:23:00.000Z","msg":"可以參考紐西蘭，係2016年公投想更改國旗<br />\n因為同澳洲太似同埋唔想有米字 似殖民地<br />\n咁我地光復完先再公投更改都未遲<br />\n至少，國際會認得龍獅旗先，同埋論述方面都易入腦好多<br />\n<br />\n無左米字代表新香港， 唔係英國，更加唔係中國殖民地！"},{"pid":"ff44f13384c5c714239da5a9fcefecba000d0173","tid":2030551,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f645e04e4b10fecb4ca92b319a0f5dd8b15e49e","tid":2030551,"uid":62721,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"aa2633b664a3b64359be